@startuml mover_scenario_workflow
title Mover Scenario Workflow
actor "HR System" as HR
participant "Identity\nGovernance" as IGA
participant "EntraID" as EID
participant "Intune MDM" as MDM
participant "ServiceNow" as SN

HR -> IGA : Role change event
IGA -> EID : Update group memberships
IGA -> EID : Revoke old role claims
EID --> IGA : Membership updated
IGA -> MDM : Push new device policy
IGA -> SN : Create mover ticket
SN --> HR : Mover checklist assigned
MDM --> EID : Device compliance confirmed
IGA -> EID : Issue updated access token
@enduml
